IN THE COURT OF [court]
AT [city], MAHARASHTRA

[party_name] ................................................. Petitioner / Plaintiff

                                  VERSUS

[respondent_name] ........................................... Respondent / Defendant

                              VAKALATNAMA

Know all men by these presents that I, [party_name], son/daughter/wife of [parent_name], aged about [age] years, residing at [address], do hereby nominate, constitute and appoint Advocate [advocate_name], enrolled with the Bar Council of Maharashtra & Goa under Registration No. [bar_no], having office at the Bar Association of [city], to be my Advocate in the above suit / proceeding, and to do the following acts, deeds and things on my behalf, namely:

  1. To appear, act, plead and conduct the above proceeding and all interlocutory applications connected therewith;
  2. To present pleadings, applications, affidavits, vakalatnamas, written statements, rejoinders and other documents required to be filed;
  3. To withdraw or compromise the said proceeding, with my prior written consent only;
  4. To deposit, draw and receive money, cheques and grants on my behalf and give effectual receipts therefor;
  5. To file and take back exhibits and documents;
  6. To engage and appoint any other Advocate or Counsel as may be considered necessary by the said Advocate, the fees of any such Advocate or Counsel to be borne by me;
  7. To do all such other acts and things which the said Advocate may consider necessary or proper for the conduct of the said proceeding.

And I hereby agree to ratify and confirm all acts done by the said Advocate or his substitute by virtue of this Vakalatnama, and I undertake to pay the agreed fees and out-of-pocket expenses as they fall due.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF I have signed this Vakalatnama at [city] on this ____ day of __________, 20___.


_________________________                                _________________________
  Signature of Client                                     Accepted by Advocate
  [party_name]                                            [advocate_name]
                                                          Enr. No. [bar_no]
